{"type":"message","id":"5c555789","parentId":"1901b7b4","timestamp":"2026-02-28T15:26:04.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call-3e4da236-70c5-4e29-b22f-88824c4e983a","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n\n# Weekly Stock Report Generator\n# Runs every Saturday to generate comprehensive market report\n\nCONFIG_FILE=\"/home/kero/.openclaw/workspace/stock-analysis-config.json\"\nREPORT_FILE=\"/home/kero/.openclaw/workspace/reports/weekly-report-$(date +%Y-%m-%d).md\"\n\n# Load configuration\nif [ ! -f \"$CONFIG_FILE\" ]; then\n    echo \"Error: Configuration file not found\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# Create reports directory if it doesn't exist\nmkdir -p /home/kero/.openclaw/workspace/reports\n\necho \"Generating weekly stock report at $(date)\"\n\n# Report header\ncat > \"$REPORT_FILE\" << EOF\n# Weekly Stock Market Report - $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n## Market Performance\n- **EGX30**: [Placeholder for index value]\n- **EGX70**: [Placeholder for index value]\n- **Gold Price**: [Placeholder for gold price]\n\n## Important News This Week\n1. [Placeholder for major news item]\n2. [Placeholder for second news item]\n3. [Placeholder for third news item]\n\n## Analysis of Followed Stocks\n### Banks\n- **CIB**: [Placeholder for analysis]\n- [Other banks if any]\n\n### Gold\n- [Gold stocks analysis]\n- [Gold funds analysis]\n\n### Companies\n- [Company 1 analysis]\n- [Company 2 analysis]\n\n## New Investment Opportunities\n1. [Opportunity 1 description]\n2. [Opportunity 2 description]\n3. [Opportunity 3 description]\n\n## Monthly Investment Reminder\n- **Monthly amount**: EGP 2,000\n- **Next investment date**: [Next Saturday]\n- **Suggested allocation**: [Based on current market conditions]\n\n## Recommendations\n- [Buy/sell/hold recommendations]\n- [Risk assessment]\n\n---\n*Report generated automatically by stock analysis system*\nEOF\n\necho \"Weekly report generated: $REPORT_FILE\"\necho \"Report includes:\"\necho \"- Market performance overview\"\necho \"- Important news summary\"\necho \"- Analysis of followed stocks\"\necho \"- New investment opportunities\"\necho \"- Monthly investment reminder\"\n\n# Send report to user (placeholder)\necho \"Weekly stock report ready for review: $REPORT_FILE\"\n\n# Archive old reports (keep last 8 weeks)\nfind /home/kero/.openclaw/workspace/reports/ -name \"weekly-report-*.md\" -mtime +56 -delete 2>/dev/null","path":"/home/kero/.openclaw/workspace/cron-weekly-report.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"arcee-ai/trinity-large-preview:free","usage":{"input":16225,"output":585,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16810,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772292340518}}
